  Locus:
    Page: 69
    Verse: 5
Tags:
  - Contentment
---
Neither circumstances nor surroundings can bring contentment. Only by fitting
ourselves to meet conditions as they are, calmly and courageously, may we
hope to reconcile ourselves to our position and conditions of life.
